{
  "stem": "20711.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And by the gang came out of the building, we were already sitting in the bus.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They came in, said hello to us, and we said hello to them.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They had no idea who they are taking to Miskoic.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were very friendly.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I knew they liked my mom, who was a very attractive lady.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she kind of flirted with them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And we had a very pleasant drive into the city.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "They wanted to know where we heading.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They would take us all the way to the house.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But my mother said no, we're going to meet in a restaurant with some friends.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they dropped us off in the center of town.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they left, and then we quickly went up to my uncle's place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the meantime, from the period of picking us up at the police station and the time we arrived with the bus, he was working nonstop to make us a place, which was a cave located in a cellar.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was a big wine cellar, which was officially a bombing shelter during the war.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But he digged a hole under this bomb shelter, and luckily, he didn't have to work overly too much, because once he went down in a tunnel, he happened to fall into a natural cave.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was a size almost like this room, which was a clear space.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "He only had to make that tunnel.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "He didn't know that he will end up with that big [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So immediately, he was able to bring down woodwork and created a wood bed, bring down warm pillows and everything he could.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was two-- well, he only left this tunnel between the shelter and this cave.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he rolled a barrow over this tunnel.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
